      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This unit boasts a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline, supported by individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the internal rotating assembly. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. While the exterior shows honest signs of use consistent with its age, the hydraulic steering remains communicative and the double-VANOS system is in peak operating condition. A purist\u2019s spec designed for driver engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Regularly maintained. Reliable performance. Minor exterior wear.",
