      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great, you've found it! This beauty has been well-loved and is totally ready for its next big adventure. It runs super smooth and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for those weekend road trips or just zipping around town. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
