      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains tight, benefiting from a documented subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal valve timing. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust, providing the linear power delivery and telepathic steering feedback this chassis is renowned for.",
